          "content": "<div><br></div><div>There is a certain comfort that comes with knowing the material you use is actually grounded in real practice. Every question and explanation you study here goes through a careful check, almost like the way instructors double check care plans during clinicals. It keeps things honest. It keeps things safe. And it helps you feel like the work you are doing truly reflects what ATI and HESI expect from future nurses.</div><div><br></div><div><br></div>"
